           | vsss 2 mch d0 frc*d0
             vsps 2 mch d0 frc*d0
             vpps 2 mch d0 frc*d0
             vppp 2 mch d0 frc*d0
           @ 0 2 0 od orc
             0 2 0 od orc
             0 3 mco od orc
             0 3 mco od orc
           ! AGSP 1 -1 m mc d0 rc  0 0
